thread.title_full: Golden Eagle Coins reviewed by Timothy C. Maddocks

author: Timothy C. Maddocks
title: Timothy C. Maddocks
text: I found $9.95 shipping cost a bit excessive for four coins. $5.95 would have been much more appropriate. As I have not received my order yet, I cannot comment on the quality of the coins I ordered. However, I have been satisfied with past orders with Golden Eagle Coins.
